target: I have booked the cityroomz hotel for 2 nights, starting this Tuesday, for 6 people.

I would like to book a room there for 6 people for 2 nights, and I would like the reference number, please. <system>  What night would you like to begin your stay? <user>  I would like to stay starting Tuesday night <system>
